short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension switches to the tab with Google Meet running with the associated hotkey.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Talking to someone on Google Meet, with way too many tabs open, and need to quickly switch back to Meet? Cool. This sets up a keyboard shortcut to do that.
